#

Spiced Honey Garlic Chicken

$15
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ChickenSweetSavoryComfort Food

Description

Tender chicken coated in a sweet and savory honey garlic glaze, served with steamed veggies.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy sauce (gluten-free): 1/4 cup
  • Garlic cloves, minced: 4
  • Ginger, grated: 1 tablespoon
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Green onions, sliced: for garnish
  • Mixed vegetables (broccoli, carrots, bell pepper): 2 cups
